      {
        "id": "n3",
        "type": "canvasNode",
        "position": {
          "x": 200,
          "y": 50
        },
        "data": {
          "label": "Python Code",
          "category": "processing",
          "blockType": "python_code",
          "inputs": [
            {
              "id": "in_0",
              "label": "in_0",
              "portType": "any"
            }
          ],
          "outputs": [
            {
              "id": "out_0",
              "label": "out_0",
              "portType": "any"
            }
          ],
          "defaultParameters": {
            "code": "# === HIL Stub: Load Coefficients ===\n# Route C-out が書いた .npz を読んで kernel namespace に展開する。\n# 後段 (FPGA Compute) はこれらを n43 Route B と同じ名前で参照できる。\nimport numpy as np\nimport os\n\n_path = str(globals().get('hil_input_path', '')).strip()\nif not _path:\n    raise ValueError(\"hil_input_path is empty — set it in the file picker (var_name='hil_input_path')\")\nif not os.path.isfile(_path):\n    raise FileNotFoundError(\"Coefficients file not found: %s\" % _path)\n\n_npz = np.load(_path, allow_pickle=False)\n\n# Required arrays (Route C-out が必ず書く)\nref_chirp        = _npz['chirp_replica'].astype(np.complex64).reshape(-1)\nfir_coefficients = _npz['fir_coefficients'].astype(np.complex64)\nS_all            = _npz['S_all'].astype(np.complex64)\n\n# Scalars\nFs         = float(_npz['meta_Fs'])\nNr         = int(_npz['meta_Nr'])\nNa         = int(_npz['meta_Na'])\nR0         = float(_npz['meta_R0'])\nlam        = float(_npz['meta_lam'])\nt_r_center = float(_npz['meta_t_r_center'])\n\n# Optional golden (for verification)\ngolden_iq_data = _npz['golden_iq_data'].astype(np.complex64) if 'golden_iq_data' in _npz.files else None\n\nprint('Loaded %s' % _path)\nprint('  shapes: ref_chirp=%s  fir_coefficients=%s  S_all=%s' % (\n    ref_chirp.shape, fir_coefficients.shape, S_all.shape))\nprint('  meta: Fs=%.0f Hz  Nr=%d  Na=%d  R0=%.0f m  lam=%.4f m' % (Fs, Nr, Na, R0, lam))\nprint('  golden_iq_data: %s' % ('present %s' % (golden_iq_data.shape,) if golden_iq_data is not None else 'absent'))\n",
            "label": "Load Coefficients",
            "spec": "【HIL Stub: Load Coefficients】\nRoute C-out が書いた coeffs.npz を読んで kernel namespace に展開する。\n後段 (n7 Q-Format Config, n4/n6 FPGA Compute) はこれらを n43 Route B と同じ名前で参照できる。\n\n読むもの: chirp_replica→ref_chirp(Nr,), fir_coefficients(Na,Nr), S_all(Na,Nr),\nmeta_Fs/Nr/Na/R0/lam/t_r_center, golden_iq_data(あれば検証用)。\n注: Q-format meta (meta_Q_*) は n7 が別途読む。\n\n配線: このノード → n7 (Q-Format Config) → {n4, n6} → n5。"
          },
          "executionOrder": 3
        },
        "width": 400,
        "style": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "n4",
        "type": "canvasNode",
        "position": {
          "x": 1138.8027716088675,
          "y": 47.702603290005925
        },
        "data": {
          "label": "Python Code",
          "category": "processing",
          "blockType": "python_code",
          "inputs": [
            {
              "id": "in_0",
              "label": "in_0",
              "portType": "any"
            }
          ],
          "outputs": [
            {
              "id": "out_0",
              "label": "out_0",
              "portType": "any"
            }
          ],
          "defaultParameters": {
            "code": "# === HIL Stub: FPGA Compute (bit-exact mirror of Route B in main flow) ===\n# Stage A/B/C の Q-format 量子化 + FFT × mult × IFFT を cupy で実行。\n# n43 Route B と同じロジックでビット同一の結果を出す。\nimport numpy as np\nimport cupy as cp\nimport math\nimport time as _time\n_t0 = _time.monotonic()\n\n# --- Q-format parameters (n43 と同期させること) -----------------------------\n# Q_IN/Q_FFT/Q_OUT は \"Q-Format Config\" ノード (n7) が coeffs.npz meta から復元済み。\nif not all(k in globals() for k in ('Q_IN', 'Q_FFT', 'Q_OUT')):\n    raise NameError(\"Q_IN/Q_FFT/Q_OUT が未定義。'Q-Format Config' ノードを先に実行すること\")\nQ_IN_W,  Q_IN_F  = Q_IN      # Stage A (ADC)\nQ_FFT_W, Q_FFT_F = Q_FFT     # Stage B (FPGA datapath)\nQ_OUT_W, Q_OUT_F = Q_OUT     # Stage C (DAC)\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\ndef _qaxis(v, n_word, n_frac, scale):\n    step = 2.0 ** (-n_frac)\n    iv_max =  (1 << (n_word - 1)) - 1\n    iv_min = -(1 << (n_word - 1))\n    return cp.clip(cp.round(v * scale / step), iv_min, iv_max) * step / scale\n\ndef qz(x, n_word, n_frac, name='', mode='auto'):\n    if x.size == 0:\n        return x.astype(cp.complex64)\n    if mode == 'fixed':\n        full_scale = float(2 ** (n_word - 1 - n_frac))\n        step = 2.0 ** (-n_frac)\n        iv_max =  (1 << (n_word - 1)) - 1\n        iv_min = -(1 << (n_word - 1))\n        r_q = cp.clip(cp.round(x.real / step), iv_min, iv_max) * step\n        i_q = cp.clip(cp.round(x.imag / step), iv_min, iv_max) * step\n        peak = float(cp.maximum(cp.abs(x.real).max(), cp.abs(x.imag).max()))\n        clip_frac = float(((cp.abs(x.real) >= full_scale) | (cp.abs(x.imag) >= full_scale)).mean())\n        err2 = (x.real - r_q) ** 2 + (x.imag - i_q) ** 2\n        sig2 = (cp.abs(x) ** 2).mean()\n        snr_db = 10.0 * float(cp.log10(sig2 / (err2.mean() + 1e-30)))\n        headroom_db = 20.0 * math.log10(full_scale / peak) if peak > 0 else float('inf')\n        print('  qz[%-9s fixed] Q%d.%d  FS=%.3g  peak=%.3g  headroom=%+5.1f dB  clip=%5.2f%%  SNR=%.1f dB'\n              % (name, n_word - n_frac, n_frac, full_scale, peak, headroom_db, 100*clip_frac, snr_db))\n        return (r_q + 1j * i_q).astype(cp.complex64)\n    peak = float(cp.maximum(cp.abs(x.real).max(), cp.abs(x.imag).max()))\n    if peak == 0:\n        return x.astype(cp.complex64)\n    full_scale = float(2 ** (n_word - 1 - n_frac))\n    s = 0.95 * full_scale / peak\n    r_q = _qaxis(x.real, n_word, n_frac, s)\n    i_q = _qaxis(x.imag, n_word, n_frac, s)\n    err2 = (x.real - r_q) ** 2 + (x.imag - i_q) ** 2\n    sig2 = (cp.abs(x) ** 2).mean()\n    snr_db = 10.0 * float(cp.log10(sig2 / (err2.mean() + 1e-30)))\n    shift_bits = math.log2(s) if s > 0 else 0.0\n    print('  qz[%-9s auto ] Q%d.%d  peak=%.3g  shift=%+6.2f bits  SNR=%.1f dB'\n          % (name, n_word - n_frac, n_frac, peak, shift_bits, snr_db))\n    return (r_q + 1j * i_q).astype(cp.complex64)\n\nprint('HIL FPGA compute (GPU): Q_IN=Q%d.%d  Q_FFT=Q%d.%d  Q_OUT=Q%d.%d' % (\n    Q_IN_W - Q_IN_F, Q_IN_F, Q_FFT_W - Q_FFT_F, Q_FFT_F, Q_OUT_W - Q_OUT_F, Q_OUT_F))\n\n# H2D\n_t_xfer = _time.monotonic()\nfir_gpu   = cp.asarray(fir_coefficients)\nchirp_gpu = cp.asarray(ref_chirp.astype(np.complex64))\ncp.cuda.Stream.null.synchronize()\nprint('  H2D: fir %s + chirp %s  (%.2fs)' % (fir_gpu.shape, chirp_gpu.shape, _time.monotonic() - _t_xfer))\n\n# Stage A: fixed Q (ADC quantize)\nfir_peak = float(cp.maximum(cp.abs(fir_gpu.real).max(), cp.abs(fir_gpu.imag).max()))\nfir_pre_scale = 0.95 / fir_peak if fir_peak > 0 else 1.0\nprint('  fir_in BRAM pre-scale: 1/%.3g   (block-scale shift = %+.2f bits)' % (\n    1.0 / fir_pre_scale, math.log2(fir_pre_scale)))\nfir_q   = qz(fir_gpu * fir_pre_scale, Q_IN_W, Q_IN_F, 'fir_in',   mode='fixed') / fir_pre_scale\nchirp_q = qz(chirp_gpu,               Q_IN_W, Q_IN_F, 'chirp_in', mode='fixed')\ndel fir_gpu, chirp_gpu\n\n# Stage B: FFT × mult (BFP auto)\nF    = qz(cp.fft.fft(fir_q, axis=1), Q_FFT_W, Q_FFT_F, 'fir_fft')\nC    = qz(cp.fft.fft(chirp_q),       Q_FFT_W, Q_FFT_F, 'chirp_fft')\nprod = qz(F * C[None, :],            Q_FFT_W, Q_FFT_F, 'prod')\ndel fir_q, chirp_q, F, C\n\n# Stage C: IFFT (BFP auto)\ns_raw_gpu = qz(cp.fft.ifft(prod, axis=1), Q_OUT_W, Q_OUT_F, 'out')\ndel prod\n\n# D2H\n_t_xfer = _time.monotonic()\ns_raw_fpga = cp.asnumpy(s_raw_gpu).astype(np.complex64)\ndel s_raw_gpu\ncp.get_default_memory_pool().free_all_blocks()\nprint('  D2H: s_raw_fpga %s  (%.2fs)' % (s_raw_fpga.shape, _time.monotonic() - _t_xfer))\n\nprint('HIL FPGA compute: s_raw_fpga=%s peak|s|=%.3f  (%.2fs total)' % (\n    s_raw_fpga.shape, float(np.abs(s_raw_fpga).max()), _time.monotonic() - _t0))\n\n# Optional: report vs golden (if Route C-out included golden_iq_data)\nif golden_iq_data is not None:\n    _diff = s_raw_fpga - golden_iq_data\n    _err_rms = float(np.sqrt(np.mean(np.abs(_diff) ** 2)))\n    _sig_rms = float(np.sqrt(np.mean(np.abs(golden_iq_data) ** 2)))\n    _snr_db  = 20.0 * np.log10(_sig_rms / (_err_rms + 1e-30))\n    _peak_err = float(np.abs(_diff).max())\n    _peak_sig = float(np.abs(golden_iq_data).max())\n    print('  vs golden: RMS err = %.4g  signal RMS = %.4g  SNR = %.1f dB  peak err / peak = %.3f%%' % (\n        _err_rms, _sig_rms, _snr_db, 100 * _peak_err / max(_peak_sig, 1e-30)))\n",
            "label": "FPGA Compute (mirror of Route B)",
            "spec": "【HIL FPGA Compute (cupy mirror of Route B)】\n\n役割: n43 Route B とビット同一の Q-format 量子化を cupy GPU で高速に実行 (~0.1s/frame)。\nHIL ループの「速い参照」。ゲートレベル厳密性は n6 (Verilator) が担う。\n\n処理: Stage A (fixed Q = ADC 量子化) → Stage B (FFT × 乗算、BFP auto) →\nStage C (IFFT、BFP auto)。fir は BRAM pre-scale (1/peak×0.95) で fixed Q に入れる。\n\n入力 (kernel): fir_coefficients (Na,Nr), ref_chirp (Nr,), Q_IN/Q_FFT/Q_OUT, golden_iq_data(任意)\n出力 (kernel): s_raw_fpga (Na,Nr) complex64 → n5 Save\n\nQ-format: ハードコードを廃止し、\"Q-Format Config\" ノード (n7) が coeffs.npz meta から\n復元した Q_IN/Q_FFT/Q_OUT を読む。→ FPGA3 n60 由来の単一ソース。\n\ngolden_iq_data があれば vs golden の RMS 誤差 / SNR を表示する。\nn6 (Verilator) とは排他 (両方 s_raw_fpga を書く)。どちらか一方だけ Enable する。"
          },
          "enabled": false
        },
        "width": 400,
        "style": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "n5",
        "type": "canvasNode",
        "position": {
          "x": 1638.8027716088675,
